latestIgtvVideos.title: Glam look✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey guys !
Wanted to do a glam look on myself like forever, tried my best. Setting my hair was challenging, every time I was done with my hair and I tried to film a hair strand popped up😂😂 I hope you guys like the look. You might be wondering what I applied on my eyelids, first I tried using Vaseline but didn’t go well so later did it from the scratch and applied some hair oil. Let me know in the comments❤️
.
